\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:255:        \"name\": \"mask_projections.1\",\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:260:        \"name\": \"mask_projections.2\",\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:265:        \"name\": \"mask_projections.3\",\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:292:        \"name\": \"mask_projections.3.2.weight\",\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:422:        \"name\": \"mask_projections.2.2.weight\",\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:442:        \"name\": \"project_visual_embed.2.weight\",\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:135:            <td><code>encoder_channels=[32,64,128,256,320]</code>，<code>decoder_layer=-1</code>，<code>num_maskformer_stages=5</code>，<code>num_heads=32</code>。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:322:      <p class=\"note\">统计方法：本地实例化 <code>VoxTellBodyModel(VoxTellBodyConfig())</code>；VoxTell 使用 v1.1 <code>plans.json</code> 的 architecture kwargs，并按推理入口设置 <code>decoder_layer=4</code>、<code>text_embedding_dim=2560</code>、<code>query_dim=2048</code>、<code>num_heads=32</code>、<code>deep_supervision=False</code>。由于当前环境缺少 <code>positional_encodings</code> 包，统计 VoxTell 参数时仅 stub 了固定 positional buffer；该 buffer 不是 trainable parameter，不影响上述参数量。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_standalone_dependency_audit_2026-05-23.html:172:Body-Tell/train.py:34 from body_tell.models.voxtell_body_model import VoxTellBodyConfig, VoxTellBodyModel</pre>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:224:            <td>Mask projections（含 <code>num_heads</code>）</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:225:            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> 两层根因：(1) Body-Tell 配置写 5，但运行时被 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截成 4 级；(2) Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）vs VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell_model.py:74</code>）。两者乘积决定实际 projection 输出。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:226:            <td>Body-Tell 实际输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>（<code>channels × 32</code>，stage 0 例外）；VoxTell 实际输出 <strong><code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级</strong>（<code>channels × 1</code>）。<strong>原报告写 VoxTell 最高级 <code>10240</code> 是错误的。</strong> 即使 encoder 升到 6 级、stage 截断消除，<code>num_heads</code> 不同会导致 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与下游 mask fusion 模块的 shape 不匹配，权重无法直接复用。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:270:            <td><code>project_bottleneck_embed</code></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:271:            <td>使用 VoxTell 命名，替代当前 <code>project_visual_embed</code>；结构仍为 <code>320 -&gt; 2048 -&gt; 2048</code>。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:272:            <td>直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_bottleneck_embed.*</code>。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:280:            <td><code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> + <code>num_heads</code></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:281:            <td>使用 VoxTell 命名，替代当前 <code>mask_projections</code>；5 级；输出维度 = encoder 各级 channels × <code>num_heads</code>。<strong>条件性对齐</strong>（父表 #13，域差异豁免）：如果实验目标是<strong>直接复用 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 和 mask fusion 权重</strong>，则必须设 <code>num_heads=1</code>，实际输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级；如果仅做结构对齐而不复用这部分权重（更符合 Body-Tell occupancy grid 任务的需求，因为 <code>num_heads=32</code> 提供 32× mask fusion 容量是为该任务调过的），则保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:282:            <td>选 <code>num_heads=1</code>：直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code>。选保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>：必须把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 全部加入跳过白名单，并在 audit 中登记\"为保留 Body-Tell mask fusion 容量而跳过这部分权重复用\"。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:298:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 新增）<code>num_heads</code> 与 projection shape 显式审计</strong>：新增 <code>Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code>（如果与已有 <code>scripts/parameter_audit.py</code> 重合，应共享 utilities）。<strong>脚本第一步必须打印两侧 <code>num_heads</code> 值和每级 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> 实际输出 shape</strong>，确认 VoxTell 为 <code>num_heads=1</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级，Body-Tell 当前为 <code>num_heads=32</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>。该审计是父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（路径 A vs 路径 B）的输入材料，audit 完成后才能在 P4 选定路径。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:303:      <p>验收：当前轻量模型仍可跑旧测试；新增审计能明确报告哪些 key 会加载、哪些 key 因 policy 跳过；<strong>且 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（设为 1 / 保留 32）必须先于 P4 落地</strong>。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:331:      <h3>P4：对齐 projection、mask head、<code>num_heads</code> 决议和 forward 排列</h3>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:332:      <div class=\"callout warnbox\"><strong>P4 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（父表 #13，域差异豁免）</strong>：在执行 P4 前必须先选定路径——\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:334:          <li><strong>路径 A（强对齐，复用权重）</strong>：<code>num_heads=1</code>，projection 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>，可直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重。代价：失去 Body-Tell 现有 32× mask fusion 容量。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:335:          <li><strong>路径 B（结构对齐但放弃这部分权重复用，推荐）</strong>：保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，projection 输出维持 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>（encoder 升 6 级后扩展），<code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重 <strong>不加载</strong>，加入 P6 跳过白名单。理由：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid 与 VoxTell 医学影像任务差异显著，这部分权重的可迁移性弱，而 mask fusion 容量对当前任务更有价值。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:337:        默认建议路径 B，并在 P0 audit 中显式打印决议来源。如果 audit 没有给出明确收益对比，<strong>保持现状（路径 B）即可，不强制对齐 <code>num_heads</code></strong>。\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:340:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）<code>num_heads</code> 决议生效</strong>：按上方选定路径执行。路径 A 需把配置 <code>num_heads</code> 默认值改为 <code>1</code>，同时审计 Body-Tell 中所有依赖 <code>num_heads</code> 的 reshape（如 <code>view(B, num_heads, C//num_heads)</code>）和 decoder stage 内 <code>input_features + num_heads</code> 的通道拼接是否正确退化；路径 B 不改 <code>num_heads</code>，但需要在 P6 把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 加入跳过白名单。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:341:        <li>把当前 <code>project_visual_embed</code> 改为 VoxTell 命名 <code>project_bottleneck_embed</code>；把 <code>mask_projections</code> 改为 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code>。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:346:      <p>验收：5 个 projection 输出维度按选定路径（路径 A: <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>；路径 B: <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>）；非立方输入的输出 shape 与 target mask 完全一致；mask fusion 模块在选定 <code>num_heads</code> 下有显式单测；audit 报告记录选定路径与原因。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:374:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）显式 <code>unexpected_keys</code> 白名单</strong>：调用 <code>model.load_state_dict(state_dict, strict=False)</code> 后，断言 <code>set(unexpected_keys) ⊆ POLICY_ALLOWED_SKIP</code>（默认 <code>{\"pos_embed\"}</code>；若 P4 决定保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，再扩展到 <code>{\"pos_embed\", \"project_to_decoder_channels.*\", \"decoder.<mask_fusion_keys>\"}</code>）。<strong>任何 shape mismatch 必须抛错，不得静默跳过</strong>；<code>missing_keys</code> 不为空时打印完整列表并要求显式确认。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:480:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 上调）P0 <code>num_heads</code> 与 projection shape 审计</strong>。这是父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 决议的输入材料；不在 P4 落地前完成审计，P3/P4/P6 都会建立在未经确认的输出维度假设上。允许 audit 结论是\"保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>\"（路径 B），但必须显式记录。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:181:    <p class=\"note warn\">2026-05-24 修订：原 11 项基础上新增 #12 BCE+Dice loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code> mismatch（Body-Tell=32 vs VoxTell=1）。其中 #13 同时修正了原 SP-A 中\"VoxTell projection 输出 <code>[32,2048,4096,8192,10240]</code>\"的错误表述（实际为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320]</code> 量级，<code>num_heads</code> 才是根因）。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:182:    <div class=\"note warn\"><strong>域差异豁免（2026-05-24 重要约束）</strong>：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid，VoxTell 处理医学影像（CT/MRI/PET）。任务输入模态、特征统计、噪声特性都不同。<strong>本计划中\"对齐\"是手段不是目的，目的是支持 VoxTell 权重复用与实现一致性。任何一项不一致，若实现阶段 audit 后发现对齐会损害性能、或对当前任务没有可观察收益、或与权重复用无关，允许显式跳过并在子计划中记录原因。</strong> #12（loss 公式）与 #13（<code>num_heads</code>）尤其适用此豁免。</div>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:227:    <p>按下面顺序开工。SP-C 不需要整体等到 SP-A/SP-B 完成；只有 deep supervision、长训通过和最终评估需要等结构与 patch-level sampler 到位。<strong>（2026-05-24 修订）阶段 1 新增 SP-A P0 audit 作为首项；阶段 2 P4 内部包含 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议（路径 A vs 路径 B），决议依赖 P0 audit 输出；阶段 3 Task 5 与 P6 的具体实现内容随 P4 决议变化。</strong></p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:242:              <li><strong><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P0</a>（新增首项）</strong>：建立兼容性基线 audit—— <code>num_heads</code> + projection shape 双侧打印、transformer golden test、weight key audit。产出三份输入材料：(a) 父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议输入，(b) P1 transformer parity 验收测试，(c) P6 权重加载白名单。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:249:          <td>形成可复现训练 loop 骨架；<strong>完成 P0 后必须显式记录 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议（默认路径 B：保留 32）</strong>；但还不能宣称 paper-aligned 长训通过。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:255:              <li>SP-A P2-P5：Residual encoder、VoxTellDecoder、projection/forward 排列、位置编码策略（<code>dynamic_hwd</code> 默认，适配 <code>[129,108,256]</code>）。<strong>P4 内部按 P0 选定的 <code>num_heads</code> 路径执行</strong>——路径 A 改 <code>num_heads=1</code>；路径 B 保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 加入 P6 跳过白名单候选。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:268:              <li>SP-A P6：VoxTell v1.1 权重加载入口与 smoke。<strong>跳过白名单按 P4 决议组装</strong>——路径 A 仅含 <code>pos_embed</code>；路径 B 额外含 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion key。<code>unexpected_keys</code> 必须完全等于白名单，否则抛错。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:288:    <p class=\"note warn\">关键路径串行依赖（2026-05-24 修订后）：<strong>SP-A P0 audit → P4 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议 → P6 跳过白名单</strong>；<strong>SP-A P3 → SP-C Task 5</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3/4 → Step 5 → Step 6</strong>。其余环节可并行。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:293:    <p>下表是本文件的核心。每一项不一致都必须被某一个子计划领走；当前 13 项已全部分发，其中结构类由 SP-A 负责（含 #13 <code>num_heads</code>，标记为条件性对齐），数据构造类由 SP-B 负责，训练机制与评估协议类由 SP-C 负责（含 #12 loss 等价性，标记为 audit 后可跳过）。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:378:          <td><span class=\"tag warn\"><code>num_heads</code> mismatch<br><span class=\"small\">（条件性对齐）</span></span></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:379:          <td>VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:74</code>）；Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）。projection 输出 = <code>channels × num_heads</code>，因此原 SP-A \"VoxTell 输出 <code>10240</code>\"的说法错误，实际为 <code>320</code> 量级。<strong>域差异豁免</strong>：<code>num_heads=32</code> 给 Body-Tell mask fusion 提供 32× 容量，是为 occupancy grid 任务设计的；强行降到 1 可能损害 capacity。<strong>对齐前提</strong>：只有在\"目标是直接复用 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重\"的实验中才必要；若仅做结构对齐（不复用这部分权重），可以保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，但<strong>必须在 SP-A P0 audit 中显式打印 num_heads 并把这些 key 加入跳过白名单</strong>，避免错误判断为权重已加载。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:380:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P0 + P4 — num_heads 审计与对齐决议</a></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:403:    <p class=\"note\">关键串行依赖（2026-05-24 修订后）：<strong>SP-A P0 audit → P4 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议 → P6 跳过白名单组装</strong>；<strong>SP-A P0 transformer golden test → P1 验收</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3 / Step 4</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 4 → Step 5 → Step 6</strong>；<strong>SP-A P3 → SP-C Task 5 deep supervision</strong>；<strong>SP-A P2/P3/P4 → SP-A P6</strong>。SP-A 结构对齐与 SP-B 数据构造可并行，但二者必须早于 deep supervision、权重加载和正式长训。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:417:        <li><strong>结构闸门</strong>（SP-A P0 完成后）：<code>audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code> 报告 transformer parity test 通过（输出差异 &lt; <code>1e-6</code>，dropout=0）；<code>num_heads</code> 与每级 projection 实际 shape 已显式打印。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:418:        <li><strong>权重加载闸门</strong>（SP-A P6 完成后）：<code>strict=False</code> 加载 VoxTell <code>checkpoint_final.pth</code> 时，<code>unexpected_keys</code> 集合等于 P4 决议产出的<strong>显式白名单</strong>——路径 A 为 <code>{\"pos_embed\"}</code>，路径 B 为 <code>{\"pos_embed\"} ∪ {project_to_decoder_channels.*, mask_fusion.*}</code>；<code>missing_keys</code> 为空；任何 shape mismatch 必须抛错。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:427:    <p><strong>可以按本文件开始执行。</strong> 13 项明确不一致已全部分发：SP-A 覆盖结构类（含 #13 <code>num_heads</code>），SP-B 覆盖数据构造类，SP-C 覆盖训练机制、checkpoint、评估协议和测试矩阵（含 #12 loss 等价性 audit）。<strong>#12 和 #13 适用域差异豁免</strong>：audit 后允许在保留 Body-Tell 当前实现并显式记录偏差的前提下跳过对齐。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:428:    <p>短期优先顺序是：SP-A P0（含 <code>num_heads</code> + projection 实际 shape 审计）、SP-B Step 1、SP-C Task 0-4 并行启动；随后推进 SP-A P1-P5 和 SP-B Step 2-Step 4；最后启用 SP-C Task 5（含 BCE+Dice 等价性 audit，可仅记录偏差）、权重加载、评估与训练实验。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:429:    <p class=\"small\">本报告仅维护审计与索引，未修改训练代码。2026-05-24 修订：增列 #12 loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code>（带域差异豁免），新增 baseline 评估闸门。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/PROMPT.md:15:SP-A P0: num_heads/projection shape audit, transformer golden test material, weight-key audit input.\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/PROMPT.md:21:- num_heads and projection shapes are printed for VoxTell and Body-Tell.\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:9:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_1\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,260p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"<!doctype html>\\n<html lang=\\\"zh-CN\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\">\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\\\">\\n  <title>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</title>\\n  <style>\\n    :root {\\n      --ink: #17202a;\\n      --muted: #5d6875;\\n      --line: #d8e0e7;\\n      --panel: #f6f8fa;\\n      --soft: #eef4f7;\\n      --accent: #14677b;\\n      --warn: #9a4a17;\\n      --bad: #993333;\\n      --good: #276749;\\n    }\\n\\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\\n\\n    body {\\n      margin: 0;\\n      color: var(--ink);\\n      background: #ffffff;\\n      font: 15px/1.62 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", sans-serif;\\n    }\\n\\n    header {\\n      padding: 34px 42px 24px;\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      background: #f8fbfd;\\n    }\\n\\n    main {\\n      max-width: 1220px;\\n      padding: 28px 42px 56px;\\n    }\\n\\n    h1 {\\n      margin: 0 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 30px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    h2 {\\n      margin: 30px 0 12px;\\n      font-size: 22px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    h3 {\\n      margin: 20px 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 17px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    p { margin: 8px 0; }\\n\\n    code {\\n      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;\\n      background: #edf3f7;\\n      border-radius: 4px;\\n      padding: 1px 4px;\\n      font-size: 0.92em;\\n    }\\n\\n    pre {\\n      overflow-x: auto;\\n      background: #111827;\\n      color: #f7fafc;\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      padding: 14px 16px;\\n      font-size: 13px;\\n      line-height: 1.5;\\n    }\\n\\n    pre code {\\n      background: transparent;\\n      padding: 0;\\n      color: inherit;\\n    }\\n\\n    table {\\n      width: 100%;\\n      border-collapse: collapse;\\n      margin: 12px 0 22px;\\n      font-size: 14px;\\n    }\\n\\n    th, td {\\n      padding: 9px 10px;\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      vertical-align: top;\\n    }\\n\\n    th {\\n      text-align: left;\\n      background: #f1f5f8;\\n      color: #24313d;\\n    }\\n\\n    ul, ol { padding-left: 22px; }\\n    li { margin: 5px 0; }\\n\\n    .meta { color: var(--muted); }\\n    .num {\\n      text-align: right;\\n      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\n    }\\n\\n    .cards {\\n      display: grid;\\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr));\\n      gap: 12px;\\n      margin: 16px 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    .card {\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      background: var(--panel);\\n      padding: 14px 16px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .card span {\\n      display: block;\\n      color: var(--muted);\\n      font-size: 13px;\\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .card strong {\\n      color: var(--accent);\\n      display: block;\\n      font-size: 22px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .callout {\\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);\\n      background: var(--soft);\\n      padding: 12px 14px;\\n      margin: 12px 0 18px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .warnbox {\\n      border-left-color: var(--warn);\\n      background: #fff7ed;\\n    }\\n\\n    .badbox {\\n      border-left-color: var(--bad);\\n      background: #fff5f5;\\n    }\\n\\n    .tag {\\n      display: inline-block;\\n      border-radius: 999px;\\n      padding: 1px 8px;\\n      font-size: 12px;\\n      font-weight: 650;\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\n    }\\n\\n    .ok { color: var(--good); background: #eaf7ef; }\\n    .warn { color: var(--warn); background: #fff2df; }\\n    .bad { color: var(--bad); background: #ffe7e7; }\\n    .info { color: var(--accent); background: #e7f3f7; }\\n\\n    @media (max-width: 860px) {\\n      header, main {\\n        padding-left: 20px;\\n        padding-right: 20px;\\n      }\\n      table {\\n        display: block;\\n        overflow-x: auto;\\n        white-space: nowrap;\\n      }\\n    }\\n  </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n  <header>\\n    <h1>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</h1>\\n    <p class=\\\"meta\\\">日期：2026-05-24；目标：让 Body-Tell 在结构和权重语义上尽量对齐 VoxTell v1.1，优先支持 VoxTell checkpoint 复用，而不是只做到 tensor shape 能加载。</p>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main>\\n    <section>\\n      <h2>核验结论</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"callout\\\">\\n        <p><strong>原差异报告中的核心不一致真实存在。</strong> 其中最影响 VoxTell 权重复用的是两类问题：一类是参数量和模块拓扑明显不同，例如 encoder/decoder；另一类是参数 shape 一致但 forward 语义不同，例如 transformer decoder。</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"cards\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>Body-Tell 当前参数</span><strong>328.98M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>VoxTell v1.1 参数</span><strong>440.03M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>Body encoder</span><strong>8.49M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>VoxTell encoder</span><strong>90.30M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>Transformer 参数</span><strong>251.86M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>最高风险</span><strong>shape 同而语义不同</strong></div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <table>\\n        <thead>\\n          <tr><th>差异点</th><th>核验结果</th><th>对权重复用的影响</th><th>证据位置</th></tr>\\n        </thead>\\n        <tbody>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Transformer decoder</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 使用 <code>activation=\\\"gelu\\\"</code>，pre-norm path 执行 self-attention；VoxTell 默认 <code>relu</code>，active <code>forward_pre</code> 跳过 self-attention，只做 cross-attention 和 FFN。</td>\\n            <td>参数名和 shape 可 100% 对上，但加载 VoxTell 权重后语义不等价。小模型同权重实验输出最大绝对差为 <code>0.9258</code>。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:69</code>、<code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:137</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:224</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Encoder backbone</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 5-stage 手写 ConvBlock；VoxTell 是 6-stage <code>ResidualEncoder</code>，features 为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320,320]</code>，blocks 为 <code>[1,3,4,6,6,6]</code>。</td>\\n            <td>当前 encoder 无法复用 VoxTell encoder 权重，也很可能限制性能上限。这个差异不是“轻量配置”，而是 backbone 类型不同。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:155</code>、<code>VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1/plans.json:20</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:131</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Mask projections（含 <code>num_heads</code>）</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> 两层根因：(1) Body-Tell 配置写 5，但运行时被 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截成 4 级；(2) Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）vs VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell_model.py:74</code>）。两者乘积决定实际 projection 输出。</td>\\n            <td>Body-Tell 实际输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>（<code>channels × 32</code>，stage 0 例外）；VoxTell 实际输出 <strong><code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级</strong>（<code>channels × 1</code>）。<strong>原报告写 VoxTell 最高级 <code>10240</code> 是错误的。</strong> 即使 encoder 升到 6 级、stage 截断消除，<code>num_heads</code> 不同会导致 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与下游 mask fusion 模块的 shape 不匹配，权重无法直接复用。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>、<code>:83</code>、<code>:89</code>；<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:74</code>、<code>:177</code>、<code>:370</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Decoder</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 4-stage 手写 decoder，<code>GroupNorm + GELU</code>；VoxTell 是 5-stage <code>VoxTellDecoder</code>，使用 <code>StackedConvBlocks</code> 并继承 encoder 的 <code>InstanceNorm3d + LeakyReLU + conv_bias=true</code>。</td>\\n            <td>当前 decoder 无法复用 VoxTell decoder 权重。VoxTell 还总是构造 <code>seg_layers</code>，用于 checkpoint 兼容。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:174</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:280</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Position / memory 排列</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag warn\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 动态生成 <code>D,H,W</code> 顺序的位置编码；VoxTell 使用 init 时固定的 <code>pos_embed</code> buffer，并用 <code>H,W,D</code> 顺序 flatten。</td>\\n            <td>Body-Tell 当前 <code>volume_size=[129,108,256]</code>（见 <code>configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:25</code>，2026-05-24 commit <code>5c31e57</code> 后裁剪到此尺寸）不是 192³，直接加载 VoxTell <code>pos_embed</code> 会遇到 shape/语义问题。需要明确动态重建或改成 192³ profile。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:118</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:185</code>、<code>:229</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n        </tbody>\\n      </table>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <section>\\n      <h2>目标状态</h2>\\n      <p>新增一个 VoxTell-aligned 架构路径，而不是在现有轻量模型上做零散补丁。该路径的 state dict 命名应尽量贴近 VoxTell，降低权重加载映射复杂度。</p>\\n\\n      <table>\\n        <thead>\\n          <tr><th>模块</th><th>目标实现</th><th>权重复用要求</th></tr>\\n        </thead>\\n        <tbody>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>encoder</code></td>\\n            <td>使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual_encoders.ResidualEncoder</code>，参数与 VoxTell v1.1 plan 一致。</td>\\n            <td>加载 VoxTell <code>encoder.*</code> 权重，shape mismatch 必须报错。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>decoder</code></td>\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:10:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_2\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,220p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"<!doctype html>\\n<html lang=\\\"zh-CN\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\">\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\\\">\\n  <title>Body-Tell 与 VoxTell 论文不一致项总控计划</title>\\n  <style>\\n    :root {\\n      --bg: #f6f7f9;\\n      --panel: #ffffff;\\n      --ink: #172033;\\n      --muted: #5c6678;\\n      --line: #d9dee8;\\n      --head: #eef2f7;\\n      --code: #f1f4f8;\\n      --red: #b3261e;\\n      --amber: #8a5a00;\\n      --green: #187044;\\n      --blue: #2459a8;\\n    }\\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\\n    body {\\n      margin: 0;\\n      background: var(--bg);\\n      color: var(--ink);\\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", \\\"Noto Sans CJK SC\\\", \\\"Microsoft YaHei\\\", sans-serif;\\n      line-height: 1.62;\\n    }\\n    main {\\n      max-width: 1180px;\\n      margin: 0 auto;\\n      padding: 36px 24px 60px;\\n    }\\n    header {\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      padding-bottom: 22px;\\n      margin-bottom: 22px;\\n    }\\n    h1 {\\n      margin: 0 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 30px;\\n      line-height: 1.25;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n    h2 {\\n      margin: 0 0 14px;\\n      font-size: 20px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n    h3 {\\n      margin: 18px 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 16px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n    p { margin: 8px 0; }\\n    section {\\n      background: var(--panel);\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      padding: 22px;\\n      margin: 18px 0;\\n    }\\n    table {\\n      width: 100%;\\n      border-collapse: collapse;\\n      margin: 10px 0 2px;\\n      font-size: 14px;\\n    }\\n    th, td {\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      padding: 10px 12px;\\n      vertical-align: top;\\n      text-align: left;\\n    }\\n    th {\\n      background: var(--head);\\n      font-weight: 650;\\n    }\\n    code {\\n      background: var(--code);\\n      border-radius: 4px;\\n      padding: 1px 5px;\\n      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, \\\"Liberation Mono\\\", monospace;\\n      font-size: 0.94em;\\n    }\\n    ul, ol {\\n      margin: 8px 0;\\n      padding-left: 22px;\\n    }\\n    li { margin: 5px 0; }\\n    .meta {\\n      color: var(--muted);\\n      font-size: 14px;\\n    }\\n    .cards {\\n      display: grid;\\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));\\n      gap: 12px;\\n      margin-top: 16px;\\n    }\\n    .card {\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      padding: 14px;\\n      background: #fbfcfe;\\n    }\\n    .card strong {\\n      display: block;\\n      color: var(--muted);\\n      font-size: 13px;\\n      font-weight: 600;\\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\\n    }\\n    .card span {\\n      display: block;\\n      font-size: 20px;\\n      font-weight: 760;\\n    }\\n    .bad { color: var(--red); }\\n    .warn { color: var(--amber); }\\n    .ok { color: var(--green); }\\n    .note {\\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);\\n      padding: 10px 12px;\\n      background: #eef5ff;\\n      border-radius: 4px;\\n      margin-top: 12px;\\n    }\\n    .note.warn {\\n      border-left-color: var(--amber);\\n      background: #fff5db;\\n    }\\n    .note.bad {\\n      border-left-color: var(--red);\\n      background: #fdeeee;\\n    }\\n    .tag {\\n      display: inline-block;\\n      border-radius: 999px;\\n      padding: 2px 8px;\\n      font-size: 12px;\\n      font-weight: 700;\\n      background: #eef2f7;\\n      color: #39445a;\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\n    }\\n    .tag.bad { background: #fdeeee; color: var(--red); }\\n    .tag.warn { background: #fff5db; color: var(--amber); }\\n    .tag.ok { background: #e9f7ef; color: var(--green); }\\n    .tag.info { background: #e7f0ff; color: var(--blue); }\\n    .small { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }\\n    a { color: var(--blue); }\\n    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\\n    .child-link {\\n      font-weight: 650;\\n      text-decoration: none;\\n      border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--blue);\\n    }\\n    @media (max-width: 900px) {\\n      main { padding: 24px 14px 42px; }\\n      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\\n      table { font-size: 13px; }\\n      th, td { padding: 8px; }\\n    }\\n    @media (max-width: 560px) {\\n      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n    }\\n  </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n<main>\\n  <header>\\n    <h1>Body-Tell 与 VoxTell 论文不一致项总控计划</h1>\\n    <p class=\\\"meta\\\">日期：2026-05-24。范围：<code>VoxTell/VoxTell.pdf</code>、<code>VoxTell/</code> 官方实现/权重计划、当前 <code>Body-Tell/</code> 训练相关代码与配置。根目录 <code>train.py</code> 未纳入。</p>\\n    <div class=\\\"cards\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>明确不一致</strong><span class=\\\"bad\\\">13 项</span></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>已分发到子计划</strong><span class=\\\"ok\\\">13 项</span></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>已起草子计划</strong><span class=\\\"ok\\\">3 个</span></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>总体判断</strong><span class=\\\"warn\\\">可执行，待实施（2026-05-24 修订）</span></div>\\n    </div>\\n    <p class=\\\"note warn\\\">2026-05-24 修订：原 11 项基础上新增 #12 BCE+Dice loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code> mismatch（Body-Tell=32 vs VoxTell=1）。其中 #13 同时修正了原 SP-A 中\\\"VoxTell projection 输出 <code>[32,2048,4096,8192,10240]</code>\\\"的错误表述（实际为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320]</code> 量级，<code>num_heads</code> 才是根因）。</p>\\n    <div class=\\\"note warn\\\"><strong>域差异豁免（2026-05-24 重要约束）</strong>：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid，VoxTell 处理医学影像（CT/MRI/PET）。任务输入模态、特征统计、噪声特性都不同。<strong>本计划中\\\"对齐\\\"是手段不是目的，目的是支持 VoxTell 权重复用与实现一致性。任何一项不一致，若实现阶段 audit 后发现对齐会损害性能、或对当前任务没有可观察收益、或与权重复用无关，允许显式跳过并在子计划中记录原因。</strong> #12（loss 公式）与 #13（<code>num_heads</code>）尤其适用此豁免。</div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <section>\\n    <h2>使用方式</h2>\\n    <p>本文件是父级执行总控，只回答三件事：先做什么、每个差异由哪个子计划负责、什么时候可以进入下一阶段。代码级方案、测试命令和参数细节以三个子计划为准。</p>\\n    <p class=\\\"note\\\">域适配差异（输入模态、patch size、augmentation、global batch、数据/词表规模等）视为 Body-Tell 前提，不作为本轮整改目标。本轮只处理可在 Body-Tell 域内对齐的模型结构、数据构造和训练机制。</p>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <section>\\n    <h2>子计划索引</h2>\\n    <table>\\n      <thead>\\n        <tr>\\n          <th>编号</th>\\n          <th>子计划</th>\\n          <th>关注范围</th>\\n          <th>状态</th>\\n        </tr>\\n      </thead>\\n      <tbody>\\n        <tr>\\n          <td>SP-A</td>\\n          <td><a class=\\\"child-link\\\" href=\\\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\\\">Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</a></td>\\n          <td>模型结构对齐：transformer decoder 语义、ResidualEncoder、VoxTellDecoder、5-scale projection、位置编码策略、VoxTell 权重加载入口、训练实验矩阵。</td>\\n          <td><span class=\\\"tag ok\\\">已起草</span></td>\\n        </tr>\\n        <tr>\\n          <td>SP-B</td>\\n          <td><a class=\\\"child-link\\\" href=\\\"bodytell_sampling_vocabulary_optimization_report.html\\\">Body-Tell Sampling 与 Vocabulary 优化思路</a></td>\\n          <td>数据构造对齐：动态采样基础设施、85% foreground patch oversampling、patch 内 2+1 prompt、25/75 canonical/variant、aggregate sampler、vocabulary expansion、text embedding 重建。</td>\\n          <td><span class=\\\"tag ok\\\">已起草</span></td>\\n        </tr>\\n        <tr>\\n          <td>SP-C</td>\\n          <td><a class=\\\"child-link\\\" href=\\\"bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\\\">Body-Tell 训练机制与评估协议对齐计划</a></td>\\n          <td>训练循环对齐：fixed-update epoch/iteration 节奏、SGD + polynomial decay、deep supervision 5-scale loss 权重、checkpoint/scheduler resume、prompt robustness / negative / held-out 评估协议、paper-aligned 测试矩阵。</td>\\n          <td><span class=\\\"tag ok\\\">已起草</span></td>\\n        </tr>\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:14:{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_6\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'rg -n \\\"SP-A|P0|golden|whitelist|weight|audit|num_heads|project\\\" Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:16:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_6\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'rg -n \\\"SP-A|P0|golden|whitelist|weight|audit|num_heads|project\\\" Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"/bin/bash: rg: command not found\\n\",\"exit_code\":127,\"status\":\"failed\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:20:{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_9\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"grep -nE \\\\\\\"SP-A|P0|golden|whitelist|weight|audit|num_heads|project\\\\\\\" Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html | sed -n '1,220p'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:24:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_9\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"grep -nE \\\\\\\"SP-A|P0|golden|whitelist|weight|audit|num_heads|project\\\\\\\" Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html | sed -n '1,220p'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"162:      font-weight: 650;\\n221:            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:155</code>、<code>VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1/plans.json:20</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:131</code></td>\\n224:            <td>Mask projections（含 <code>num_heads</code>）</td>\\n225:            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> 两层根因：(1) Body-Tell 配置写 5，但运行时被 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截成 4 级；(2) Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）vs VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell_model.py:74</code>）。两者乘积决定实际 projection 输出。</td>\\n226:            <td>Body-Tell 实际输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>（<code>channels × 32</code>，stage 0 例外）；VoxTell 实际输出 <strong><code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级</strong>（<code>channels × 1</code>）。<strong>原报告写 VoxTell 最高级 <code>10240</code> 是错误的。</strong> 即使 encoder 升到 6 级、stage 截断消除，<code>num_heads</code> 不同会导致 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与下游 mask fusion 模块的 shape 不匹配，权重无法直接复用。</td>\\n270:            <td><code>project_bottleneck_embed</code></td>\\n271:            <td>使用 VoxTell 命名，替代当前 <code>project_visual_embed</code>；结构仍为 <code>320 -&gt; 2048 -&gt; 2048</code>。</td>\\n272:            <td>直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_bottleneck_embed.*</code>。</td>\\n275:            <td><code>project_text_embed</code></td>\\n277:            <td>直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_text_embed.*</code>。</td>\\n280:            <td><code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> + <code>num_heads</code></td>\\n281:            <td>使用 VoxTell 命名，替代当前 <code>mask_projections</code>；5 级；输出维度 = encoder 各级 channels × <code>num_heads</code>。<strong>条件性对齐</strong>（父表 #13，域差异豁免）：如果实验目标是<strong>直接复用 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 和 mask fusion 权重</strong>，则必须设 <code>num_heads=1</code>，实际输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级；如果仅做结构对齐而不复用这部分权重（更符合 Body-Tell occupancy grid 任务的需求，因为 <code>num_heads=32</code> 提供 32× mask fusion 容量是为该任务调过的），则保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>。</td>\\n282:            <td>选 <code>num_heads=1</code>：直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code>。选保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>：必须把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 全部加入跳过白名单，并在 audit 中登记\\\"为保留 Body-Tell mask fusion 容量而跳过这部分权重复用\\\"。</td>\\n296:      <h3>P0：建立兼容性基线</h3>\\n298:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 新增）<code>num_heads</code> 与 projection shape 显式审计</strong>：新增 <code>Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code>（如果与已有 <code>scripts/parameter_audit.py</code> 重合，应共享 utilities）。<strong>脚本第一步必须打印两侧 <code>num_heads</code> 值和每级 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> 实际输出 shape</strong>，确认 VoxTell 为 <code>num_heads=1</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级，Body-Tell 当前为 <code>num_heads=32</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>。该审计是父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（路径 A vs 路径 B）的输入材料，audit 完成后才能在 P4 选定路径。</li>\\n300:        <li>新增 transformer golden test <code>Body-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py</code>：同一小尺寸 state dict、相同输入、dropout=0 时，Body-Tell aligned transformer 输出必须与 VoxTell transformer 完全一致或在 <code>1e-6</code> 内。</li>\\n301:        <li>新增 weight key audit：读取 <code>VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1/fold_0/checkpoint_final.pth</code>（已确认文件存在）的 <code>network_weights</code>，检查除 <code>pos_embed</code> 外的目标 key 是否全部可加载。</li>\\n303:      <p>验收：当前轻量模型仍可跑旧测试；新增审计能明确报告哪些 key 会加载、哪些 key 因 policy 跳过；<strong>且 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（设为 1 / 保留 32）必须先于 P4 落地</strong>。</p>\\n331:      <h3>P4：对齐 projection、mask head、<code>num_heads</code> 决议和 forward 排列</h3>\\n332:      <div class=\\\"callout warnbox\\\"><strong>P4 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（父表 #13，域差异豁免）</strong>：在执行 P4 前必须先选定路径——\\n334:          <li><strong>路径 A（强对齐，复用权重）</strong>：<code>num_heads=1</code>，projection 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>，可直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重。代价：失去 Body-Tell 现有 32× mask fusion 容量。</li>\\n335:          <li><strong>路径 B（结构对齐但放弃这部分权重复用，推荐）</strong>：保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，projection 输出维持 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>（encoder 升 6 级后扩展），<code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重 <strong>不加载</strong>，加入 P6 跳过白名单。理由：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid 与 VoxTell 医学影像任务差异显著，这部分权重的可迁移性弱，而 mask fusion 容量对当前任务更有价值。</li>\\n337:        默认建议路径 B，并在 P0 audit 中显式打印决议来源。如果 audit 没有给出明确收益对比，<strong>保持现状（路径 B）即可，不强制对齐 <code>num_heads</code></strong>。\\n340:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）<code>num_heads</code> 决议生效</strong>：按上方选定路径执行。路径 A 需把配置 <code>num_heads</code> 默认值改为 <code>1</code>，同时审计 Body-Tell 中所有依赖 <code>num_heads</code> 的 reshape（如 <code>view(B, num_heads, C//num_heads)</code>）和 decoder stage 内 <code>input_features + num_heads</code> 的通道拼接是否正确退化；路径 B 不改 <code>num_heads</code>，但需要在 P6 把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 加入跳过白名单。</li>\\n341:        <li>把当前 <code>project_visual_embed</code> 改为 VoxTell 命名 <code>project_bottleneck_embed</code>；把 <code>mask_projections</code> 改为 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code>。</li>\\n342:        <li>encoder 变为 6-stage 后，projection stage 自然恢复为 5 级，不再用 <code>len(encoder_channels)-1</code> 隐式截断配置。</li>\\n346:      <p>验收：5 个 projection 输出维度按选定路径（路径 A: <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>；路径 B: <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>）；非立方输入的输出 shape 与 target mask 完全一致；mask fusion 模块在选定 <code>num_heads</code> 下有显式单测；audit 报告记录选定路径与原因。</p>\\n372:        <li>新增训练参数 <code>--init-from-voxtell VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1</code>，在 optimizer 构造前加载。</li>\\n373:        <li>新增 loader：读取 <code>fold_0/checkpoint_final.pth</code> 的 <code>network_weights</code>，按当前 aligned 模型 key 直接加载。</li>\\n374:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）显式 <code>unexpected_keys</code> 白名单</strong>：调用 <code>model.load_state_dict(state_dict, strict=False)</code> 后，断言 <code>set(unexpected_keys) ⊆ POLICY_ALLOWED_SKIP</code>（默认 <code>{\\\"pos_embed\\\"}</code>；若 P4 决定保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，再扩展到 <code>{\\\"pos_embed\\\", \\\"project_to_decoder_channels.*\\\", \\\"decoder.<mask_fusion_keys>\\\"}</code>）。<strong>任何 shape mismatch 必须抛错，不得静默跳过</strong>；<code>missing_keys</code> 不为空时打印完整列表并要求显式确认。</li>\\n400:            <td>只加载 transformer / text / projection 权重</td>\\n406:            <td>加载 encoder、decoder、projection、transformer；按 policy 跳过或加载 <code>pos_embed</code></td>\\n420:python Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py \\\\\\n422:  --voxtell-dir VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1 \\\\\\n429:  --init-from-voxtell ../VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1 \\\\\\n480:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 上调）P0 <code>num_heads</code> 与 projection shape 审计</strong>。这是父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 决议的输入材料；不在 P4 落地前完成审计，P3/P4/P6 都会建立在未经确认的输出维度假设上。允许 audit 结论是\\\"保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>\\\"（路径 B），但必须显式记录。</li>\\n484:        <li><strong>最后才跑完整训练实验。</strong> 没有 architecture/weight audit 通过前，不建议直接用 VoxTell checkpoint warm-start 长训。</li>\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:31:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_15\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,220p' Body-Tell/scripts/parameter_audit.py\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"#!/usr/bin/env python3\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"Audit Body-Tell model parameter counts and emit an HTML report.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport argparse\\nimport html\\nimport importlib.util\\nimport json\\nimport re\\nimport sys\\nfrom collections import defaultdict\\nfrom dataclasses import asdict\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nfrom typing import Any\\n\\nimport torch\\nimport yaml\\n\\n\\nREPO_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[2]\\nBODY_TELL_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\\nif str(BODY_TELL_ROOT) not in sys.path:\\n    sys.path.insert(0, str(BODY_TELL_ROOT))\\n\\n\\ndef load_body_train_module() -> Any:\\n    train_path = BODY_TELL_ROOT / \\\"train.py\\\"\\n    spec = importlib.util.spec_from_file_location(\\\"body_tell_train_entry\\\", train_path)\\n    if spec is None or spec.loader is None:\\n        raise RuntimeError(f\\\"Cannot import training entry from {train_path}\\\")\\n    module = importlib.util.module_from_spec(spec)\\n    spec.loader.exec_module(module)\\n    return module\\n\\n\\ndef human_count(value: int) -> str:\\n    if value >= 1_000_000_000:\\n        return f\\\"{value / 1_000_000_000:.3f}B\\\"\\n    if value >= 1_000_000:\\n        return f\\\"{value / 1_000_000:.3f}M\\\"\\n    if value >= 1_000:\\n        return f\\\"{value / 1_000:.3f}K\\\"\\n    return str(value)\\n\\n\\ndef bytes_to_gib(value: int) -> float:\\n    return value / (1024**3)\\n\\n\\ndef module_param_count(model: torch.nn.Module, prefix: str) -> tuple[int, int]:\\n    module = model.get_submodule(prefix) if prefix else model\\n    total = sum(param.numel() for param in module.parameters())\\n    trainable = sum(param.numel() for param in module.parameters() if param.requires_grad)\\n    return total, trainable\\n\\n\\ndef direct_child_counts(model: torch.nn.Module) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\\n    rows = []\\n    for name, child in model.named_children():\\n        total = sum(param.numel() for param in child.parameters())\\n        trainable = sum(param.numel() for param in child.parameters() if param.requires_grad)\\n        rows.append({\\\"name\\\": name, \\\"total\\\": total, \\\"trainable\\\": trainable})\\n    return rows\\n\\n\\ndef subtree_counts(model: torch.nn.Module) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\\n    prefixes = [\\n        \\\"encoder\\\",\\n        \\\"encoder.stages.0\\\",\\n        \\\"encoder.stages.1\\\",\\n        \\\"encoder.stages.2\\\",\\n        \\\"encoder.stages.3\\\",\\n        \\\"encoder.stages.4\\\",\\n        \\\"project_visual_embed\\\",\\n        \\\"project_text_embed\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder.layers.0\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder.layers.1\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder.layers.2\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder.layers.3\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder.layers.4\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder.layers.5\\\",\\n        \\\"transformer_decoder.norm\\\",\\n        \\\"mask_projections\\\",\\n        \\\"mask_projections.0\\\",\\n        \\\"mask_projections.1\\\",\\n        \\\"mask_projections.2\\\",\\n        \\\"mask_projections.3\\\",\\n        \\\"decoder\\\",\\n        \\\"decoder.upconvs\\\",\\n        \\\"decoder.blocks\\\",\\n        \\\"decoder.seg_layers\\\",\\n    ]\\n    rows = []\\n    for prefix in prefixes:\\n        try:\\n            total, trainable = module_param_count(model, prefix)\\n        except AttributeError:\\n            continue\\n        rows.append({\\\"name\\\": prefix, \\\"total\\\": total, \\\"trainable\\\": trainable})\\n    return rows\\n\\n\\ndef parameter_rows(model: torch.nn.Module) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\\n    rows = []\\n    for name, param in model.named_parameters():\\n        rows.append(\\n            {\\n                \\\"name\\\": name,\\n                \\\"shape\\\": tuple(int(x) for x in param.shape),\\n                \\\"numel\\\": int(param.numel()),\\n                \\\"requires_grad\\\": bool(param.requires_grad),\\n                \\\"dtype\\\": str(param.dtype).replace(\\\"torch.\\\", \\\"\\\"),\\n            }\\n        )\\n    return sorted(rows, key=lambda item: item[\\\"numel\\\"], reverse=True)\\n\\n\\ndef top_level_from_name(name: str) -> str:\\n    return name.split(\\\".\\\", 1)[0]\\n\\n\\ndef category_counts(param_rows: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\\n    grouped: dict[str, dict[str, int]] = defaultdict(lambda: {\\\"total\\\": 0, \\\"trainable\\\": 0})\\n    for row in param_rows:\\n        key = top_level_from_name(row[\\\"name\\\"])\\n        grouped[key][\\\"total\\\"] += row[\\\"numel\\\"]\\n        if row[\\\"requires_grad\\\"]:\\n            grouped[key][\\\"trainable\\\"] += row[\\\"numel\\\"]\\n    return [\\n        {\\\"name\\\": name, \\\"total\\\": counts[\\\"total\\\"], \\\"trainable\\\": counts[\\\"trainable\\\"]}\\n        for name, counts in sorted(grouped.items(), key=lambda item: item[1][\\\"total\\\"], reverse=True)\\n    ]\\n\\n\\ndef find_logged_parameter_count(log_path: Path | None) -> int | None:\\n    if not log_path or not log_path.exists():\\n        return None\\n    pattern = re.compile(r\\\"Model parameters:\\\\s*([0-9,]+)\\\")\\n    for line in log_path.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\", errors=\\\"replace\\\").splitlines():\\n        match = pattern.search(line)\\n        if match:\\n            return int(match.group(1).replace(\\\",\\\", \\\"\\\"))\\n    return None\\n\\n\\ndef parse_training_metrics(log_path: Path | None) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\\n    if not log_path or not log_path.exists():\\n        return None\\n    epoch_pattern = re.compile(\\n        r\\\"Epoch\\\\s+(\\\\d+).*?loss=([0-9.]+).*?dice=([0-9.]+).*?fg_dice=([0-9.]+).*?neg_fp=([0-9.]+)\\\"\\n    )\\n    val_pattern = re.compile(\\n        r\\\"\\\\[val\\\\]\\\\s+loss=([0-9.]+)\\\\s+\\\\|\\\\s+fg_dice=([0-9.]+)\\\\s+\\\\|\\\\s+neg_fp=([0-9.]+)\\\"\\n    )\\n    train_rows = []\\n    val_rows = []\\n    for line in log_path.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\", errors=\\\"replace\\\").splitlines():\\n        epoch_match = epoch_pattern.search(line)\\n        if epoch_match:\\n            train_rows.append(\\n                {\\n                    \\\"epoch\\\": int(epoch_match.group(1)),\\n                    \\\"loss\\\": float(epoch_match.group(2)),\\n                    \\\"dice_loss\\\": float(epoch_match.group(3)),\\n                    \\\"fg_dice\\\": float(epoch_match.group(4)),\\n                    \\\"neg_fp\\\": float(epoch_match.group(5)),\\n                }\\n            )\\n            continue\\n        val_match = val_pattern.search(line)\\n        if val_match:\\n            val_rows.append(\\n                {\\n                    \\\"epoch\\\": len(val_rows) + 1,\\n                    \\\"loss\\\": float(val_match.group(1)),\\n                    \\\"fg_dice\\\": float(val_match.group(2)),\\n                    \\\"neg_fp\\\": float(val_match.group(3)),\\n                }\\n            )\\n    if not train_rows and not val_rows:\\n        return None\\n    return {\\\"train\\\": train_rows, \\\"val\\\": val_rows}\\n\\n\\ndef pct(value: int, total: int) -> str:\\n    if total == 0:\\n        return \\\"0.00%\\\"\\n    return f\\\"{100 * value / total:.2f}%\\\"\\n\\n\\ndef row_html(row: dict[str, Any], total: int) -> str:\\n    return (\\n        \\\"<tr>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td><code>{html.escape(str(row['name']))}</code></td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td class=\\\\\\\"num\\\\\\\">{row['total']:,}</td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td class=\\\\\\\"num\\\\\\\">{human_count(row['total'])}</td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td class=\\\\\\\"num\\\\\\\">{pct(row['total'], total)}</td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td class=\\\\\\\"num\\\\\\\">{row['trainable']:,}</td>\\\"\\n        \\\"</tr>\\\"\\n    )\\n\\n\\ndef param_row_html(row: dict[str, Any], total: int) -> str:\\n    return (\\n        \\\"<tr>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td><code>{html.escape(row['name'])}</code></td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td><code>{html.escape(str(row['shape']))}</code></td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td class=\\\\\\\"num\\\\\\\">{row['numel']:,}</td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td class=\\\\\\\"num\\\\\\\">{pct(row['numel'], total)}</td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td>{html.escape(row['dtype'])}</td>\\\"\\n        f\\\"<td>{'yes' if row['requires_grad'] else 'no'}</td>\\\"\\n        \\\"</tr>\\\"\\n    )\\n\\n\\ndef render_report(audit: dict[str, Any]) -> str:\\n    total = audit[\\\"totals\\\"][\\\"parameters\\\"]\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:32:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_12\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '250,430p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"        <thead>\\n          <tr><th>模块</th><th>目标实现</th><th>权重复用要求</th></tr>\\n        </thead>\\n        <tbody>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>encoder</code></td>\\n            <td>使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual_encoders.ResidualEncoder</code>，参数与 VoxTell v1.1 plan 一致。</td>\\n            <td>加载 VoxTell <code>encoder.*</code> 权重，shape mismatch 必须报错。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>decoder</code></td>\\n            <td>移植 VoxTell <code>VoxTellDecoder</code>，保留 5 个 stage、<code>StackedConvBlocks</code>、<code>seg_layers</code> always-built 语义。</td>\\n            <td>加载 VoxTell <code>decoder.*</code> 权重；为了严格兼容，可保留 <code>self.encoder = encoder</code> 这一共享引用。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>transformer_decoder</code></td>\\n            <td>与 VoxTell 的 <code>TransformerDecoderLayer</code> 行为一致：默认 <code>relu</code>，pre-norm 不执行 self-attention。</td>\\n            <td>同名加载 VoxTell transformer 权重；保留 self-attention 参数，即使 active path 不使用。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>project_bottleneck_embed</code></td>\\n            <td>使用 VoxTell 命名，替代当前 <code>project_visual_embed</code>；结构仍为 <code>320 -&gt; 2048 -&gt; 2048</code>。</td>\\n            <td>直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_bottleneck_embed.*</code>。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>project_text_embed</code></td>\\n            <td>保持 <code>2560 -&gt; 2048 -&gt; 2048</code>。</td>\\n            <td>直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_text_embed.*</code>。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> + <code>num_heads</code></td>\\n            <td>使用 VoxTell 命名，替代当前 <code>mask_projections</code>；5 级；输出维度 = encoder 各级 channels × <code>num_heads</code>。<strong>条件性对齐</strong>（父表 #13，域差异豁免）：如果实验目标是<strong>直接复用 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 和 mask fusion 权重</strong>，则必须设 <code>num_heads=1</code>，实际输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级；如果仅做结构对齐而不复用这部分权重（更符合 Body-Tell occupancy grid 任务的需求，因为 <code>num_heads=32</code> 提供 32× mask fusion 容量是为该任务调过的），则保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>。</td>\\n            <td>选 <code>num_heads=1</code>：直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code>。选保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>：必须把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 全部加入跳过白名单，并在 audit 中登记\\\"为保留 Body-Tell mask fusion 容量而跳过这部分权重复用\\\"。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>pos_embed</code></td>\\n            <td>提供两种 policy：<code>dynamic_hwd</code> 用于当前非 192³ Body-Tell 输入；<code>fixed_voxtell_192</code> 用于严格复刻 VoxTell patch。</td>\\n            <td><code>dynamic_hwd</code> 模式跳过 checkpoint 中 <code>pos_embed</code>；<code>fixed_voxtell_192</code> 模式要求 shape 完全匹配。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n        </tbody>\\n      </table>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <section>\\n      <h2>实施阶段</h2>\\n\\n      <h3>P0：建立兼容性基线</h3>\\n      <ol>\\n        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 新增）<code>num_heads</code> 与 projection shape 显式审计</strong>：新增 <code>Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code>（如果与已有 <code>scripts/parameter_audit.py</code> 重合，应共享 utilities）。<strong>脚本第一步必须打印两侧 <code>num_heads</code> 值和每级 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> 实际输出 shape</strong>，确认 VoxTell 为 <code>num_heads=1</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级，Body-Tell 当前为 <code>num_heads=32</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>。该审计是父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（路径 A vs 路径 B）的输入材料，audit 完成后才能在 P4 选定路径。</li>\\n        <li>实例化 Body-Tell aligned model 和 VoxTell v1.1 model，输出总参数、模块参数、state dict key/shape 覆盖率。</li>\\n        <li>新增 transformer golden test <code>Body-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py</code>：同一小尺寸 state dict、相同输入、dropout=0 时，Body-Tell aligned transformer 输出必须与 VoxTell transformer 完全一致或在 <code>1e-6</code> 内。</li>\\n        <li>新增 weight key audit：读取 <code>VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1/fold_0/checkpoint_final.pth</code>（已确认文件存在）的 <code>network_weights</code>，检查除 <code>pos_embed</code> 外的目标 key 是否全部可加载。</li>\\n      </ol>\\n      <p>验收：当前轻量模型仍可跑旧测试；新增审计能明确报告哪些 key 会加载、哪些 key 因 policy 跳过；<strong>且 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（设为 1 / 保留 32）必须先于 P4 落地</strong>。</p>\\n\\n      <h3>P1：先修 transformer decoder 语义</h3>\\n      <ol>\\n        <li>把 <code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py</code> 的 active <code>forward_pre</code> 改为 VoxTell 版本：从 <code>norm2 -&gt; cross_attn -&gt; norm3 -&gt; FFN</code> 开始，不执行 self-attention。</li>\\n        <li>构造层时去掉 <code>activation=\\\"gelu\\\"</code>，或显式设为 <code>relu</code>，与 VoxTell 默认一致。</li>\\n        <li>保留 <code>self_attn</code>、<code>norm1</code> 等参数名和 shape，保证 checkpoint key 不变。</li>\\n      </ol>\\n      <p>验收：Body-Tell aligned transformer 与 VoxTell transformer 小模型 parity test 通过；加载 VoxTell <code>transformer_decoder.*</code> 后无 missing/unexpected/shape mismatch。</p>\\n\\n      <h3>P2：替换 encoder 为 VoxTell residual encoder</h3>\\n      <ol>\\n        <li>新增配置文件 <code>Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_aligned.yaml</code>，设置 <code>encoder_channels: [32,64,128,256,320,320]</code>、<code>n_blocks_per_stage: [1,3,4,6,6,6]</code>、<code>decoder_layer: 4</code>、<code>num_maskformer_stages: 5</code>。</li>\\n        <li>在模型配置中加入 <code>architecture: voxtell_v1_1</code> 或 <code>backbone: residual_encoder</code>，让旧轻量模型和 aligned 模型可并存。</li>\\n        <li>使用 VoxTell 相同构造参数：<code>conv_bias=true</code>、<code>InstanceNorm3d(eps=1e-5, affine=True)</code>、<code>LeakyReLU(inplace=True)</code>、<code>BasicBlockD</code>、<code>return_skips=True</code>、<code>disable_default_stem=False</code>。</li>\\n        <li>把依赖写入 Body-Tell 环境声明：<code>dynamic-network-architectures&gt;=0.4.1,&lt;0.5</code> 和 <code>einops</code>。若采用 VoxTell 原始位置编码实现，再加入 <code>positional-encodings</code>。</li>\\n      </ol>\\n      <p>验收：encoder 参数约 <code>90.30M</code>；输出 6 个 skip；<code>encoder.output_channels</code> 和 <code>encoder.strides</code> 与 VoxTell 一致；VoxTell <code>encoder.*</code> 权重可加载。</p>\\n\\n      <h3>P3：替换 decoder 为 VoxTellDecoder</h3>\\n      <ol>\\n        <li>移植 <code>VoxTellDecoder</code> 到 Body-Tell 模型代码或独立模块，优先保持源码结构、字段名和 state dict key 兼容。</li>\\n        <li>使用 <code>n_conv_per_stage_decoder=[1,1,1,1,1]</code>，并继承 encoder 的 conv/norm/nonlin/dropout/bias。</li>\\n        <li>即使 <code>deep_supervision=false</code>，也总是构造 5 个 <code>seg_layers</code>，与 VoxTell checkpoint 兼容。</li>\\n        <li>移除 Body-Tell 当前 decoder 中 upconv 后的自动 <code>F.interpolate</code> fallback；如果输入尺寸不能通过转置卷积对齐，应在测试中显式暴露，或在数据裁剪 policy 中解决。</li>\\n      </ol>\\n      <p>验收：decoder 本体参数约 <code>12.18M</code>；5 个 stage / 5 个 transposed conv / 5 个 seg layer；VoxTell <code>decoder.*</code> 权重可加载。统计 decoder 参数时需扣除共享 encoder，避免误读为 <code>102.47M</code>。</p>\\n\\n      <h3>P4：对齐 projection、mask head、<code>num_heads</code> 决议和 forward 排列</h3>\\n      <div class=\\\"callout warnbox\\\"><strong>P4 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（父表 #13，域差异豁免）</strong>：在执行 P4 前必须先选定路径——\\n        <ul>\\n          <li><strong>路径 A（强对齐，复用权重）</strong>：<code>num_heads=1</code>，projection 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>，可直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重。代价：失去 Body-Tell 现有 32× mask fusion 容量。</li>\\n          <li><strong>路径 B（结构对齐但放弃这部分权重复用，推荐）</strong>：保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，projection 输出维持 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>（encoder 升 6 级后扩展），<code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重 <strong>不加载</strong>，加入 P6 跳过白名单。理由：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid 与 VoxTell 医学影像任务差异显著，这部分权重的可迁移性弱，而 mask fusion 容量对当前任务更有价值。</li>\\n        </ul>\\n        默认建议路径 B，并在 P0 audit 中显式打印决议来源。如果 audit 没有给出明确收益对比，<strong>保持现状（路径 B）即可，不强制对齐 <code>num_heads</code></strong>。\\n      </div>\\n      <ol>\\n        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）<code>num_heads</code> 决议生效</strong>：按上方选定路径执行。路径 A 需把配置 <code>num_heads</code> 默认值改为 <code>1</code>，同时审计 Body-Tell 中所有依赖 <code>num_heads</code> 的 reshape（如 <code>view(B, num_heads, C//num_heads)</code>）和 decoder stage 内 <code>input_features + num_heads</code> 的通道拼接是否正确退化；路径 B 不改 <code>num_heads</code>，但需要在 P6 把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 加入跳过白名单。</li>\\n        <li>把当前 <code>project_visual_embed</code> 改为 VoxTell 命名 <code>project_bottleneck_embed</code>；把 <code>mask_projections</code> 改为 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code>。</li>\\n        <li>encoder 变为 6-stage 后，projection stage 自然恢复为 5 级，不再用 <code>len(encoder_channels)-1</code> 隐式截断配置。</li>\\n        <li>forward 中使用 VoxTell 的 memory 排列：<code>b c d h w -&gt; b h w d c -&gt; (h w d) b c</code>。</li>\\n        <li>decoder 输出仍保持 Body-Tell 训练和推理需要的 <code>(B, N, D, H, W)</code> 语义；如果内部沿用 VoxTell 注释中的 <code>h,w,d</code> 命名，需要在单测里用非立方输入验证轴没有被误换。</li>\\n      </ol>\\n      <p>验收：5 个 projection 输出维度按选定路径（路径 A: <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>；路径 B: <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>）；非立方输入的输出 shape 与 target mask 完全一致；mask fusion 模块在选定 <code>num_heads</code> 下有显式单测；audit 报告记录选定路径与原因。</p>\\n\\n      <h3>P5：位置编码策略</h3>\\n      <table>\\n        <thead>\\n          <tr><th>策略</th><th>适用场景</th><th>实现方式</th><th>权重加载</th></tr>\\n        </thead>\\n        <tbody>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>dynamic_hwd</code></td>\\n            <td>推荐用于当前 Body-Tell 数据，因为 <code>[129,108,256]</code>（commit <code>5c31e57</code> 后的实际 crop 尺寸）不是 VoxTell 的 192³ patch。</td>\\n            <td>按 selected feature 的实时 <code>H,W,D</code> 生成 deterministic 3D positional encoding，并缓存到 device/dtype。</td>\\n            <td>跳过 VoxTell checkpoint 的 <code>pos_embed</code>，其余权重严格加载。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>fixed_voxtell_192</code></td>\\n            <td>用于做完全复刻实验，或想验证整份 VoxTell state dict 可严格加载。</td>\\n            <td>把 Body-Tell 数据裁剪/填充到 <code>[192,192,192]</code>，注册 shape 为 <code>(1728,1,2048)</code> 的 <code>pos_embed</code>。</td>\\n            <td>要求 checkpoint 中 <code>pos_embed</code> 直接加载；数据体素尺寸也必须配套调整。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n        </tbody>\\n      </table>\\n      <p>建议先落地 <code>dynamic_hwd</code>。它牺牲的是固定 buffer 的逐元素复用，不牺牲 transformer 权重语义；对当前非立方 Body-Tell 数据更可实现。</p>\\n\\n      <h3>P6：权重加载入口</h3>\\n      <ol>\\n        <li>新增训练参数 <code>--init-from-voxtell VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1</code>，在 optimizer 构造前加载。</li>\\n        <li>新增 loader：读取 <code>fold_0/checkpoint_final.pth</code> 的 <code>network_weights</code>，按当前 aligned 模型 key 直接加载。</li>\\n        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）显式 <code>unexpected_keys</code> 白名单</strong>：调用 <code>model.load_state_dict(state_dict, strict=False)</code> 后，断言 <code>set(unexpected_keys) ⊆ POLICY_ALLOWED_SKIP</code>（默认 <code>{\\\"pos_embed\\\"}</code>；若 P4 决定保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，再扩展到 <code>{\\\"pos_embed\\\", \\\"project_to_decoder_channels.*\\\", \\\"decoder.<mask_fusion_keys>\\\"}</code>）。<strong>任何 shape mismatch 必须抛错，不得静默跳过</strong>；<code>missing_keys</code> 不为空时打印完整列表并要求显式确认。</li>\\n        <li>日志记录 loaded tensor 数、loaded 参数数、skipped key、missing key、unexpected key，并写入训练 checkpoint 的 <code>config.init_from_voxtell</code>。</li>\\n        <li>不要把旧 Body-Tell checkpoint 与 aligned 模型静默混用。旧 checkpoint 应只用于旧架构；aligned checkpoint 应带 <code>architecture: voxtell_v1_1</code>。</li>\\n      </ol>\\n      <p>验收：在 CPU 上能完成权重加载审计；<code>unexpected_keys</code> 与 policy 白名单一致；在 GPU 上能完成至少 1 个 batch 的 forward/loss/backward smoke。</p>\\n\\n      <h3>P7：训练实验矩阵</h3>\\n      <table>\\n        <thead>\\n          <tr><th>实验</th><th>初始化</th><th>目的</th><th>建议</th></tr>\\n        </thead>\\n        <tbody>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>A：当前基线</td>\\n            <td>现有轻量 Body-Tell checkpoint</td>\\n            <td>保持可回退基线。</td>\\n            <td>记录当前 val foreground Dice 约 <code>0.3257</code>。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>B：aligned random</td>\\n            <td>VoxTell-aligned 结构，随机初始化</td>\\n            <td>分离“结构变大”与“VoxTell 权重”的收益。</td>\\n            <td>先跑短程，确认显存和 loss 曲线。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>C：aligned prompt-only</td>\\n            <td>只加载 transformer / text / projection 权重</td>\\n            <td>评估 prompt decoder 复用本身的收益。</td>\\n            <td>可作为中间回退，因为 encoder 输入域差异最大。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>D：aligned full</td>\\n            <td>加载 encoder、decoder、projection、transformer；按 policy 跳过或加载 <code>pos_embed</code></td>\\n            <td>完整复用 VoxTell 权重，验证性能上限。</td>\\n            <td>使用分组学习率：prompt/transformer 较低，encoder/decoder 可稍高；不要一开始冻结全部 encoder。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n        </tbody>\\n      </table>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <section>\\n      <h2>验收命令</h2>\\n      <pre><code># 1. Transformer 行为必须与 VoxTell 对齐\\npython -m pytest Body-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py\\n\\n# 2. 架构和 state dict key/shape 审计\\npython Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py \\\\\\n  --config Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_aligned.yaml \\\\\\n  --voxtell-dir VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1 \\\\\\n  --pos-embed-policy dynamic_hwd\\n\\n# 3. 训练 smoke，验证 forward/loss/backward/checkpoint\\ncd Body-Tell\\npython train.py \\\\\\n  --config configs/phase1_voxtell_aligned.yaml \\\\\\n  --init-from-voxtell ../VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1 \\\\\\n  --smoke --epochs 2 --batch-size 1 --num-workers 0 --amp\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:33:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_13\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,260p' Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\\\"\\\"\\\"VoxTell-style prompt-conditioned model adapted for Body-Tell occupancy grids.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport math\\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\\nfrom typing import List, Sequence, Tuple\\n\\nimport torch\\nimport torch.nn.functional as F\\nfrom torch import Tensor, nn\\n\\nfrom .transformer import TransformerDecoder, TransformerDecoderLayer\\n\\n\\n@dataclass(frozen=True)\\nclass VoxTellBodyConfig:\\n    input_channels: int = 1\\n    encoder_channels: Tuple[int, ...] = (32, 64, 128, 256, 320)\\n    text_embedding_dim: int = 2560\\n    query_dim: int = 2048\\n    text_projection_hidden_dim: int = 2048\\n    transformer_num_heads: int = 8\\n    transformer_layers: int = 6\\n    transformer_feedforward_dim: int = 2048\\n    transformer_dropout: float = 0.1\\n    decoder_layer: int = -1\\n    num_maskformer_stages: int = 5\\n    num_heads: int = 32\\n    deep_supervision: bool = False\\n\\n\\nclass VoxTellBodyModel(nn.Module):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Prompt-conditioned binary mask model using VoxTell-style dynamic heads.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    def __init__(self, config: VoxTellBodyConfig | None = None) -> None:\\n        super().__init__()\\n        self.config = config or VoxTellBodyConfig()\\n        if self.config.query_dim % self.config.transformer_num_heads != 0:\\n            raise ValueError(\\\"query_dim must be divisible by transformer_num_heads\\\")\\n        if len(self.config.encoder_channels) < 2:\\n            raise ValueError(\\\"encoder_channels must contain at least two stages\\\")\\n        if self.config.num_maskformer_stages < 1:\\n            raise ValueError(\\\"num_maskformer_stages must be at least 1 for the dynamic mask head\\\")\\n\\n        self.encoder = _BodyEncoder(\\n            input_channels=self.config.input_channels,\\n            channels=self.config.encoder_channels,\\n        )\\n        selected_stage = self.config.decoder_layer\\n        if selected_stage < 0:\\n            selected_stage = len(self.config.encoder_channels) + selected_stage\\n        if selected_stage < 0 or selected_stage >= len(self.config.encoder_channels):\\n            raise ValueError(\\\"decoder_layer selects no encoder stage\\\")\\n        self.selected_stage = selected_stage\\n\\n        selected_channels = self.config.encoder_channels[self.selected_stage]\\n        self.project_visual_embed = nn.Sequential(\\n            nn.Linear(selected_channels, self.config.query_dim),\\n            nn.GELU(),\\n            nn.Linear(self.config.query_dim, self.config.query_dim),\\n        )\\n        self.project_text_embed = nn.Sequential(\\n            nn.Linear(self.config.text_embedding_dim, self.config.text_projection_hidden_dim),\\n            nn.GELU(),\\n            nn.Linear(self.config.text_projection_hidden_dim, self.config.query_dim),\\n        )\\n\\n        layer = TransformerDecoderLayer(\\n            d_model=self.config.query_dim,\\n            nhead=self.config.transformer_num_heads,\\n            dim_feedforward=self.config.transformer_feedforward_dim,\\n            dropout=self.config.transformer_dropout,\\n            activation=\\\"gelu\\\",\\n            normalize_before=True,\\n        )\\n        self.transformer_decoder = TransformerDecoder(\\n            decoder_layer=layer,\\n            num_layers=self.config.transformer_layers,\\n            norm=nn.LayerNorm(self.config.query_dim),\\n        )\\n\\n        self.fused_stage_count = min(\\n            self.config.num_maskformer_stages,\\n            len(self.config.encoder_channels) - 1,\\n        )\\n        self.mask_projections = nn.ModuleList()\\n        for stage_index, channels in enumerate(self.config.encoder_channels[: self.fused_stage_count]):\\n            output_dim = channels if stage_index == 0 else channels * self.config.num_heads\\n            self.mask_projections.append(\\n                nn.Sequential(\\n                    nn.Linear(self.config.query_dim, self.config.text_projection_hidden_dim),\\n                    nn.GELU(),\\n                    nn.Linear(self.config.text_projection_hidden_dim, output_dim),\\n                )\\n            )\\n\\n        self.decoder = _VoxTellBodyDecoder(\\n            encoder_channels=self.config.encoder_channels,\\n            num_heads=self.config.num_heads,\\n            fused_stage_count=self.fused_stage_count,\\n            deep_supervision=self.config.deep_supervision,\\n        )\\n\\n    def forward(self, occupancy: Tensor, text_embeddings: Tensor) -> Tensor | List[Tensor]:\\n        if text_embeddings.ndim == 4 and text_embeddings.shape[2] == 1:\\n            text_embeddings = text_embeddings.squeeze(2)\\n        if text_embeddings.ndim != 3:\\n            raise ValueError(\\n                \\\"text_embeddings must have shape (B, N, E) or (B, N, 1, E), \\\"\\n                f\\\"got {tuple(text_embeddings.shape)}\\\"\\n            )\\n\\n        skips = self.encoder(occupancy)\\n        selected_feature = skips[self.selected_stage]\\n        batch_size, channels, depth, height, width = selected_feature.shape\\n\\n        memory = selected_feature.permute(2, 3, 4, 0, 1).reshape(-1, batch_size, channels)\\n        memory = self.project_visual_embed(memory)\\n        pos = sinusoidal_position_encoding_3d(\\n            (depth, height, width),\\n            self.config.query_dim,\\n            device=memory.device,\\n            dtype=memory.dtype,\\n        )\\n\\n        text_queries = text_embeddings.permute(1, 0, 2)\\n        text_queries = self.project_text_embed(text_queries)\\n        mask_embedding, _ = self.transformer_decoder(\\n            tgt=text_queries,\\n            memory=memory,\\n            pos=pos,\\n        )\\n        mask_embedding = mask_embedding.permute(1, 0, 2)\\n\\n        stage_embeddings = [projection(mask_embedding) for projection in self.mask_projections]\\n        num_prompts = text_embeddings.shape[1]\\n        per_prompt_outputs: List[List[Tensor]] = []\\n        for prompt_index in range(num_prompts):\\n            prompt_stage_embeddings = [\\n                embedding[:, prompt_index : prompt_index + 1, :]\\n                for embedding in stage_embeddings\\n            ]\\n            per_prompt_outputs.append(self.decoder(skips, prompt_stage_embeddings))\\n\\n        outputs = [\\n            torch.cat(scale_outputs, dim=1)\\n            for scale_outputs in zip(*per_prompt_outputs)\\n        ]\\n        if self.config.deep_supervision:\\n            return outputs\\n        return outputs[0]\\n\\n\\nclass _BodyEncoder(nn.Module):\\n    def __init__(self, input_channels: int, channels: Sequence[int]) -> None:\\n        super().__init__()\\n        stages = []\\n        current_channels = input_channels\\n        for stage_index, output_channels in enumerate(channels):\\n            stride = 1 if stage_index == 0 else 2\\n            stages.append(_ConvBlock(current_channels, output_channels, stride=stride))\\n            current_channels = output_channels\\n        self.stages = nn.ModuleList(stages)\\n\\n    def forward(self, x: Tensor) -> List[Tensor]:\\n        skips = []\\n        for stage in self.stages:\\n            x = stage(x)\\n            skips.append(x)\\n        return skips\\n\\n\\nclass _VoxTellBodyDecoder(nn.Module):\\n    def __init__(\\n        self,\\n        encoder_channels: Sequence[int],\\n        num_heads: int,\\n        fused_stage_count: int,\\n        deep_supervision: bool,\\n    ) -> None:\\n        super().__init__()\\n        self.encoder_channels = tuple(int(x) for x in encoder_channels)\\n        self.num_heads = int(num_heads)\\n        self.fused_stage_count = int(fused_stage_count)\\n        self.deep_supervision = bool(deep_supervision)\\n\\n        upconvs = []\\n        blocks = []\\n        seg_layers = []\\n        current_channels = self.encoder_channels[-1]\\n        for target_stage in reversed(range(len(self.encoder_channels) - 1)):\\n            target_channels = self.encoder_channels[target_stage]\\n            upconvs.append(\\n                nn.ConvTranspose3d(\\n                    current_channels,\\n                    target_channels,\\n                    kernel_size=2,\\n                    stride=2,\\n                )\\n            )\\n            blocks.append(_ConvBlock(target_channels * 2, target_channels))\\n\\n            uses_intermediate_fusion = self._uses_fusion(target_stage) and target_stage > 0\\n            if uses_intermediate_fusion:\\n                if self.deep_supervision:\\n                    seg_layers.append(nn.Conv3d(target_channels + self.num_heads, 1, kernel_size=1))\\n                else:\\n                    seg_layers.append(nn.Identity())\\n                current_channels = target_channels + self.num_heads\\n            else:\\n                seg_layers.append(nn.Identity())\\n                current_channels = target_channels\\n\\n        self.upconvs = nn.ModuleList(upconvs)\\n        self.blocks = nn.ModuleList(blocks)\\n        self.seg_layers = nn.ModuleList(seg_layers)\\n\\n    def forward(self, skips: Sequence[Tensor], mask_embeddings: Sequence[Tensor]) -> List[Tensor]:\\n        x = skips[-1]\\n        outputs = []\\n\\n        for decoder_index, target_stage in enumerate(reversed(range(len(skips) - 1))):\\n            skip = skips[target_stage]\\n            x = self.upconvs[decoder_index](x)\\n            if x.shape[2:] != skip.shape[2:]:\\n                x = F.interpolate(x, size=skip.shape[2:], mode=\\\"trilinear\\\", align_corners=False)\\n            x = torch.cat((x, skip), dim=1)\\n            x = self.blocks[decoder_index](x)\\n\\n            if target_stage == 0:\\n                mask_embedding = mask_embeddings[0]\\n                outputs.append(torch.einsum(\\\"b c d h w, b n c -> b n d h w\\\", x, mask_embedding))\\n                continue\\n\\n            if self._uses_fusion(target_stage):\\n                mask_embedding = mask_embeddings[target_stage]\\n                batch_size, _, channels = mask_embedding.shape\\n                mask_embedding = mask_embedding.view(batch_size, self.num_heads, channels // self.num_heads)\\n                fusion = torch.einsum(\\\"b c d h w, b n c -> b n d h w\\\", x, mask_embedding)\\n                x = torch.cat((x, fusion), dim=1)\\n                if self.deep_supervision:\\n                    outputs.append(self.seg_layers[decoder_index](x))\\n\\n        outputs = outputs[::-1]\\n        if not self.deep_supervision:\\n            return outputs[:1]\\n        return outputs\\n\\n    def _uses_fusion(self, stage_index: int) -> bool:\\n        return stage_index < self.fused_stage_count\\n\\n\\nclass _ConvBlock(nn.Module):\\n    def __init__(self, in_channels: int, out_channels: int, stride: int = 1) -> None:\\n        super().__init__()\\n        self.block = nn.Sequential(\\n            nn.Conv3d(in_channels, out_channels, kernel_size=3, stride=stride, padding=1, bias=False),\\n            nn.GroupNorm(_num_groups(out_channels), out_channels),\\n            nn.GELU(),\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:38:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_16\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,460p' VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"import torch\\nfrom torch import nn\\nfrom torch.nn.modules.conv import _ConvNd\\nfrom torch.nn.modules.dropout import _DropoutNd\\n\\nfrom typing import List, Type, Union, Tuple\\nfrom dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.helper import get_matching_convtransp\\nfrom dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.plain_conv_encoder import PlainConvEncoder\\nfrom dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual import BasicBlockD, BottleneckD\\nfrom dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual_encoders import ResidualEncoder\\nfrom dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.simple_conv_blocks import StackedConvBlocks\\nfrom dynamic_network_architectures.initialization.weight_init import InitWeights_He, init_last_bn_before_add_to_0\\nfrom einops import rearrange, repeat\\nfrom positional_encodings.torch_encodings import PositionalEncoding3D\\n\\nfrom voxtell.model.transformer import TransformerDecoder, TransformerDecoderLayer\\n\\n\\nclass VoxTellModel(nn.Module):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    VoxTell segmentation model with text-prompted decoder.\\n    \\n    This model combines a ResidualEncoder backbone with a transformer-based decoder\\n    that uses text embeddings to generate segmentation masks. It supports multi-stage\\n    decoding with optional deep supervision.\\n    \\n    Attributes:\\n        encoder: ResidualEncoder backbone for feature extraction.\\n        decoder: VoxTellDecoder for multi-scale feature decoding.\\n        transformer_decoder: Transformer for fusing text and image features.\\n        deep_supervision: Whether to return multi-scale predictions.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    \\n    # Class constants for transformer architecture (text prompt decoder)\\n    TRANSFORMER_NUM_HEADS = 8\\n    TRANSFORMER_NUM_LAYERS = 6\\n    \\n    # Decoder configuration for different stages\\n    DECODER_CONFIGS = {\\n        0: {\\\"channels\\\": 32, \\\"shape\\\": (192, 192, 192)},\\n        1: {\\\"channels\\\": 64, \\\"shape\\\": (96, 96, 96)},\\n        2: {\\\"channels\\\": 128, \\\"shape\\\": (48, 48, 48)},\\n        3: {\\\"channels\\\": 256, \\\"shape\\\": (24, 24, 24)},\\n        4: {\\\"channels\\\": 320, \\\"shape\\\": (12, 12, 12)},\\n        5: {\\\"channels\\\": 320, \\\"shape\\\": (6, 6, 6)},\\n    }\\n    \\n    def __init__(\\n        self,\\n        input_channels: int,\\n        n_stages: int,\\n        features_per_stage: Union[int, List[int], Tuple[int, ...]],\\n        conv_op: Type[_ConvNd],\\n        kernel_sizes: Union[int, List[int], Tuple[int, ...]],\\n        strides: Union[int, List[int], Tuple[int, ...]],\\n        n_blocks_per_stage: Union[int, List[int], Tuple[int, ...]],\\n        n_conv_per_stage_decoder: Union[int, Tuple[int, ...], List[int]],\\n        conv_bias: bool = False,\\n        norm_op: Union[None, Type[nn.Module]] = None,\\n        norm_op_kwargs: dict = None,\\n        dropout_op: Union[None, Type[_DropoutNd]] = None,\\n        dropout_op_kwargs: dict = None,\\n        nonlin: Union[None, Type[torch.nn.Module]] = None,\\n        nonlin_kwargs: dict = None,\\n        deep_supervision: bool = False,\\n        block: Union[Type[BasicBlockD], Type[BottleneckD]] = BasicBlockD,\\n        bottleneck_channels: Union[int, List[int], Tuple[int, ...]] = None,\\n        stem_channels: int = None,\\n        # Text-prompted segmentation parameters\\n        num_maskformer_stages: int = 5,\\n        query_dim: int = 864,\\n        decoder_layer: int = 4,\\n        text_embedding_dim: int = 1024,\\n        num_heads: int = 1,\\n        project_to_decoder_hidden_dim: int = 432\\n    ) -> None:\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        Initialize the VoxTell model.\\n        \\n        Args:\\n            input_channels: Number of input channels.\\n            n_stages: Number of encoder stages.\\n            features_per_stage: Number of features at each stage.\\n            conv_op: Convolution operation type.\\n            kernel_sizes: Kernel sizes for convolutions.\\n            strides: Strides for downsampling.\\n            n_blocks_per_stage: Number of residual blocks per stage.\\n            n_conv_per_stage_decoder: Number of convolutions per stage.\\n            conv_bias: Whether to use bias in convolutions.\\n            norm_op: Normalization operation.\\n            norm_op_kwargs: Normalization operation keyword arguments.\\n            dropout_op: Dropout operation.\\n            dropout_op_kwargs: Dropout operation keyword arguments.\\n            nonlin: Non-linearity operation.\\n            nonlin_kwargs: Non-linearity keyword arguments.\\n            deep_supervision: Whether to use deep supervision.\\n            block: Residual block type (BasicBlockD or BottleneckD).\\n            bottleneck_channels: Channels in bottleneck layers.\\n            stem_channels: Channels in stem layer.\\n            num_maskformer_stages: Number of stages to fuse text-image embeddings in decoder.\\n            query_dim: Dimension of query embeddings.\\n            decoder_layer: Which decoder layer to use as memory for text prompt decoder (0-5).\\n            text_embedding_dim: Dimension of text embeddings.\\n            num_heads: Number of channels added per U-Net stage for mask embedding fusion.\\n            project_to_decoder_hidden_dim: Hidden dimension for projection to decoder.\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        super().__init__()\\n        if isinstance(n_blocks_per_stage, int):\\n            n_blocks_per_stage = [n_blocks_per_stage] * n_stages\\n        if isinstance(n_conv_per_stage_decoder, int):\\n            n_conv_per_stage_decoder = [n_conv_per_stage_decoder] * (n_stages - 1)\\n        \\n        assert len(n_blocks_per_stage) == n_stages, (\\n            f\\\"n_blocks_per_stage must have as many entries as we have resolution stages. \\\"\\n            f\\\"Expected: {n_stages}, got: {len(n_blocks_per_stage)} ({n_blocks_per_stage})\\\"\\n        )\\n        assert len(n_conv_per_stage_decoder) == (n_stages - 1), (\\n            f\\\"n_conv_per_stage_decoder must have one less entry than resolution stages. \\\"\\n            f\\\"Expected: {n_stages - 1}, got: {len(n_conv_per_stage_decoder)} ({n_conv_per_stage_decoder})\\\"\\n        )\\n        if num_maskformer_stages != 5:\\n            assert not deep_supervision, (\\n                \\\"Deep supervision is not supported for num_maskformer_stages != 5.\\\"\\n            )\\n        self.deep_supervision = deep_supervision\\n        self.num_heads = num_heads\\n        self.query_dim = query_dim\\n        self.project_to_decoder_hidden_dim = project_to_decoder_hidden_dim\\n        self.text_embedding_dim = text_embedding_dim\\n        \\n        # Initialize encoder backbone\\n        self.encoder = ResidualEncoder(\\n            input_channels, n_stages, features_per_stage, conv_op, kernel_sizes, strides,\\n            n_blocks_per_stage, conv_bias, norm_op, norm_op_kwargs, dropout_op,\\n            dropout_op_kwargs, nonlin, nonlin_kwargs, block, bottleneck_channels,\\n            return_skips=True, disable_default_stem=False, stem_channels=stem_channels\\n        )\\n        \\n        # Initialize decoder\\n        self.decoder = VoxTellDecoder(\\n            self.encoder, 1, n_conv_per_stage_decoder, deep_supervision,\\n            num_maskformer_stages, num_heads=self.num_heads\\n        )\\n        \\n        # Select decoder layer configuration\\n        self.selected_decoder_layer = decoder_layer\\n        if decoder_layer not in self.DECODER_CONFIGS:\\n            raise ValueError(\\n                f\\\"decoder_layer must be in {list(self.DECODER_CONFIGS.keys())}, got {decoder_layer}\\\"\\n            )\\n        selected_config = self.DECODER_CONFIGS[decoder_layer]\\n        \\n        h, w, d = selected_config[\\\"shape\\\"]\\n\\n        # Project bottleneck embeddings to query dimension\\n        self.project_bottleneck_embed = nn.Sequential(\\n            nn.Linear(selected_config[\\\"channels\\\"], query_dim),\\n            nn.GELU(),\\n            nn.Linear(query_dim, query_dim),\\n        )\\n\\n        # Project text embeddings to query dimension\\n        text_hidden_dim = 2048\\n        self.project_text_embed = nn.Sequential(\\n            nn.Linear(self.text_embedding_dim, text_hidden_dim),\\n            nn.GELU(),\\n            nn.Linear(text_hidden_dim, query_dim),\\n        )\\n\\n        # Project decoder output to image channels for each mask-former stage\\n        self.project_to_decoder_channels = nn.ModuleList([\\n            nn.Sequential(\\n                nn.Linear(query_dim, self.project_to_decoder_hidden_dim),\\n                nn.GELU(),\\n                nn.Linear(\\n                    self.project_to_decoder_hidden_dim,\\n                    decoder_config[\\\"channels\\\"] * self.num_heads if stage_idx != 0 else decoder_config[\\\"channels\\\"]\\n                )\\n            )\\n            for stage_idx, decoder_config in enumerate(\\n                list(self.DECODER_CONFIGS.values())[:num_maskformer_stages]\\n            )\\n        ])\\n        \\n        # Initialize 3D positional encoding\\n        # Shape: (H*W*D, batch_size, query_dim)\\n        pos_embed = PositionalEncoding3D(query_dim)(torch.zeros(1, h, w, d, query_dim))\\n        pos_embed = rearrange(pos_embed, 'b h w d c -> (h w d) b c')\\n        self.register_buffer('pos_embed', pos_embed)\\n\\n        # Initialize transformer decoder for fusing text and image features (prompt decoder)\\n        transformer_layer = TransformerDecoderLayer(\\n            d_model=query_dim,\\n            nhead=self.TRANSFORMER_NUM_HEADS,\\n            normalize_before=True\\n        )\\n        decoder_norm = nn.LayerNorm(query_dim)\\n        self.transformer_decoder = TransformerDecoder(\\n            decoder_layer=transformer_layer,\\n            num_layers=self.TRANSFORMER_NUM_LAYERS,\\n            norm=decoder_norm\\n        )\\n\\n    def forward(\\n        self,\\n        img: torch.Tensor,\\n        text_embedding: torch.Tensor = None\\n    ) -> Union[torch.Tensor, List[torch.Tensor]]:\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        Forward pass through VoxTell model.\\n        \\n        Args:\\n            img: Input image tensor of shape (B, C, D, H, W).\\n            text_embedding: Pre-computed text embeddings of shape (B, N, D) where\\n                N is number of prompts and D is embedding dimension.\\n            \\n        Returns:\\n            If deep_supervision is False, returns single prediction tensor of shape (B, N, D, H, W).\\n            If deep_supervision is True, returns list of prediction tensors at different scales.\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        # Extract multi-scale features from encoder\\n        skips = self.encoder(img)\\n\\n        # Select encoder features \\n        selected_feature = skips[self.selected_decoder_layer]\\n\\n        # Reshape and project features to query dimension\\n        # Shape: (B, C, D, H, W) -> (B, H, W, D, C) -> (B, H, W, D, query_dim)\\n        bottleneck_embed = rearrange(selected_feature, 'b c d h w -> b h w d c')\\n        bottleneck_embed = self.project_bottleneck_embed(bottleneck_embed)\\n        # Shape: (B, H, W, D, query_dim) -> (H*W*D, B, query_dim) for transformer\\n        bottleneck_embed = rearrange(bottleneck_embed, 'b h w d c -> (h w d) b c')\\n\\n        # Remove singleton dimension from text embeddings and project\\n        # Shape: (B, N, 1, D) -> (B, N, D)\\n        text_embedding = text_embedding.squeeze(2)\\n        # Shape: (B, N, D) -> (N, B, D) as required by transformer decoder\\n        text_embed = repeat(text_embedding, 'b n dim -> n b dim')\\n        text_embed = self.project_text_embed(text_embed)\\n\\n        # Fuse text and image features through transformer decoder\\n        # Output shape: (N, B, query_dim)\\n        mask_embedding, _ = self.transformer_decoder(\\n            tgt=text_embed,\\n            memory=bottleneck_embed,\\n            pos=self.pos_embed,\\n            memory_key_padding_mask=None\\n        )\\n        # Shape: (N, B, query_dim) -> (B, N, query_dim)\\n        mask_embedding = repeat(mask_embedding, 'n b dim -> b n dim')\\n\\n        # Project mask embeddings to decoder channel dimensions for each stage\\n        mask_embeddings = [\\n            projection(mask_embedding)\\n            for projection in self.project_to_decoder_channels\\n        ]\\n\\n        # Generate segmentation outputs for each text prompt\\n        outs = []\\n        num_prompts = text_embedding.shape[1]\\n        for prompt_idx in range(num_prompts):\\n            # Extract embeddings for this prompt across all stages\\n            prompt_embeds = [m[:, prompt_idx:prompt_idx + 1] for m in mask_embeddings]\\n            outs.append(self.decoder(skips, prompt_embeds))\\n        \\n        # Concatenate outputs across prompts for each scale\\n        outs = [torch.cat(scale_outs, dim=1) for scale_outs in zip(*outs)]\\n\\n        if not self.deep_supervision:\\n            outs = outs[0]\\n\\n        return outs\\n\\n    @staticmethod\\n    def initialize(module):\\n        InitWeights_He(1e-2)(module)\\n        init_last_bn_before_add_to_0(module)\\n\\n\\nclass VoxTellDecoder(nn.Module):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Decoder for VoxTell with mask-embedding fusion.\\n    \\n    This decoder upsamples features from the encoder and fuses them with\\n    mask embeddings from text prompts at multiple scales. It supports\\n    deep supervision for multi-scale training.\\n    \\n    The decoder processes features from bottleneck to highest resolution,\\n    incorporating mask embeddings through einsum operations at each stage.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    \\n    def __init__(\\n        self,\\n        encoder: Union[PlainConvEncoder, ResidualEncoder],\\n        num_classes: int,\\n        n_conv_per_stage: Union[int, Tuple[int, ...], List[int]],\\n        deep_supervision: bool,\\n        num_maskformer_stages: int = 5,\\n        nonlin_first: bool = False,\\n        norm_op: Union[None, Type[nn.Module]] = None,\\n        norm_op_kwargs: dict = None,\\n        dropout_op: Union[None, Type[_DropoutNd]] = None,\\n        dropout_op_kwargs: dict = None,\\n        nonlin: Union[None, Type[torch.nn.Module]] = None,\\n        nonlin_kwargs: dict = None,\\n        conv_bias: bool = None,\\n        num_heads: int = 1\\n    ) -> None:\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        Initialize VoxTell decoder.\\n        \\n        The decoder upsamples features from encoder stages and fuses them with\\n        mask embeddings. Each stage consists of:\\n        1) Transpose convolution to upsample lower resolution features\\n        2) Concatenation with skip connections from encoder\\n        3) Convolutional blocks to merge features\\n        4) Fusion with mask embeddings via einsum\\n        5) Optional segmentation output for deep supervision\\n        \\n        Args:\\n            encoder: Encoder module (PlainConvEncoder or ResidualEncoder).\\n            num_classes: Number of output classes (typically 1 for binary segmentation).\\n            n_conv_per_stage: Number of convolution blocks per decoder stage.\\n            deep_supervision: Whether to output predictions at multiple scales.\\n            num_maskformer_stages: Number of stages to fuse mask embeddings.\\n            nonlin_first: Whether to apply non-linearity before convolution.\\n            norm_op: Normalization operation (inherited from encoder if None).\\n            norm_op_kwargs: Normalization keyword arguments.\\n            dropout_op: Dropout operation (inherited from encoder if None).\\n            dropout_op_kwargs: Dropout keyword arguments.\\n            nonlin: Non-linearity operation (inherited from encoder if None).\\n            nonlin_kwargs: Non-linearity keyword arguments.\\n            conv_bias: Whether to use bias in convolutions (inherited from encoder if None).\\n            num_heads: Number of attention heads for mask embedding fusion.\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        super().__init__()\\n        self.deep_supervision = deep_supervision\\n        self.encoder = encoder\\n        self.num_classes = num_classes\\n        self.num_heads = num_heads\\n        \\n        n_stages_encoder = len(encoder.output_channels)\\n        if isinstance(n_conv_per_stage, int):\\n            n_conv_per_stage = [n_conv_per_stage] * (n_stages_encoder - 1)\\n        \\n        assert len(n_conv_per_stage) == n_stages_encoder - 1, (\\n            f\\\"n_conv_per_stage must have one less entry than encoder stages. \\\"\\n            f\\\"Expected: {n_stages_encoder - 1}, got: {len(n_conv_per_stage)}\\\"\\n        )\\n\\n        # Inherit hyperparameters from encoder if not specified\\n        transpconv_op = get_matching_convtransp(conv_op=encoder.conv_op)\\n        conv_bias = encoder.conv_bias if conv_bias is None else conv_bias\\n        norm_op = encoder.norm_op if norm_op is None else norm_op\\n        norm_op_kwargs = encoder.norm_op_kwargs if norm_op_kwargs is None else norm_op_kwargs\\n        dropout_op = encoder.dropout_op if dropout_op is None else dropout_op\\n        dropout_op_kwargs = encoder.dropout_op_kwargs if dropout_op_kwargs is None else dropout_op_kwargs\\n        nonlin = encoder.nonlin if nonlin is None else nonlin\\n        nonlin_kwargs = encoder.nonlin_kwargs if nonlin_kwargs is None else nonlin_kwargs\\n\\n        # Build decoder stages from bottleneck to highest resolution\\n        stages = []\\n        transpconvs = []\\n        seg_layers = []\\n        for stage_idx in range(1, n_stages_encoder):\\n            # Determine input channels: add num_heads for stages with mask embedding fusion\\n            if stage_idx <= n_stages_encoder - num_maskformer_stages:\\n                input_features_below = encoder.output_channels[-stage_idx]\\n            else:\\n                input_features_below = encoder.output_channels[-stage_idx] + num_heads\\n            \\n            input_features_skip = encoder.output_channels[-(stage_idx + 1)]\\n            stride_for_transpconv = encoder.strides[-stage_idx]\\n            \\n            # Transpose convolution for upsampling\\n            transpconvs.append(transpconv_op(\\n                input_features_below, input_features_skip,\\n                stride_for_transpconv, stride_for_transpconv,\\n                bias=conv_bias\\n            ))\\n            \\n            # Convolutional blocks for feature merging\\n            # Input features: 2x input_features_skip (concatenated skip + upsampled features)\\n            stages.append(StackedConvBlocks(\\n                n_conv_per_stage[stage_idx - 1], encoder.conv_op,\\n                2 * input_features_skip, input_features_skip,\\n                encoder.kernel_sizes[-(stage_idx + 1)], 1,\\n                conv_bias, norm_op, norm_op_kwargs,\\n                dropout_op, dropout_op_kwargs,\\n                nonlin, nonlin_kwargs, nonlin_first\\n            ))\\n\\n            # Segmentation output layer (always built for parameter loading compatibility)\\n            # This allows models trained with